Package model.players

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GamePlayer
    This class implements Comparable and represents players of the game.
    Goalkeeper
    This class extends GamePlayer and represents the goalkeeper of the game.
    PlayerCollection
    This class extends Iterable and represents a collection of players as an ArrayList which includes Striker and Goalkeeper.
    PlayerCollectionIterator
    This class implements Iterator and represents the iterator for the PlayerCollection.
    PlayerFactory
    This is a factory class that creates players for the soccer game as per factory pattern.
    PlayerStatistics
    This class represents player statistics either count of catches or goals scored.
    Striker
    This class represents the Striker which is a type of GamePlayer.
